---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | Mount Kush" description="Mount Kush Terms and Conditions. Cannabis lifestyle store, Johannesburg." noIndex={false}>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="display-md">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p style="margin-top:0.75rem; font-size:0.9rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">Last updated: March 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--purple-deep);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong style="color:var(--gold-bright);">Age Restriction — 18 Years and Older</strong><br/>
          By accessing this website and purchasing from Mount Kush, you confirm that you are 18 years of age or older. Mount Kush reserves the right to refuse service to any person unable to verify their age.
        </div>

        <h2>1. About Mount Kush</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush ("we", "us", "our") is a cannabis lifestyle retail brand operating physical stores in Johannesburg, South Africa. We sell cannabis accessories, lifestyle products and branded merchandise to adults 18 years and older.</p>
        <p>Our stores are located in Blackheath, Allens Nek (Roodepoort) and Berario (Randburg). All enquiries and orders are managed via WhatsApp on <strong>063 926 0217</strong>.</p>

        <h2>2. Age Verification</h2>
        <p>You must be 18 years of age or older to access this website, browse our products or place any order with Mount Kush. By using this website you confirm that you meet this age requirement.</p>
        <p>Mount Kush reserves the right to request proof of age and to refuse any sale where age cannot be verified. Age verification may be required in-store at the point of purchase.</p>

        <h2>3. Ordering Process</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush does not offer an online checkout. All orders are processed privately via WhatsApp. The ordering process is as follows:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Customer views products or categories on this website</li>
          <li>Customer contacts us via the Order via WhatsApp button</li>
          <li>We confirm product availability</li>
          <li>Customer receives a secure FNB payment link</li>
          <li>Order is confirmed upon receipt of payment</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Mount Kush reserves the right to decline any order at its sole discretion.</p>

        <h2>4. Product Information</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable steps to ensure product descriptions on this website are accurate. However, product availability, descriptions and pricing are subject to change without notice. Actual product appearance may differ slightly from images shown.</p>
        <p>Mount Kush sells cannabis accessories, lifestyle products and merchandise. We do not sell cannabis flower, cannabis derivatives or any controlled substances.</p>

        <h2>5. Payment</h2>
        <p>Payments are processed via secure FNB payment links sent through WhatsApp. Mount Kush does not store payment card details. We accept EFT and card payment via the FNB payment portal.</p>

        <h2>6. Returns and Refunds</h2>
        <p>We accept returns of unused, unopened products within 7 days of purchase with proof of purchase. Items must be in their original condition and packaging. Returns are subject to inspection.</p>
        <p>To arrange a return, contact us on WhatsApp at 063 926 0217.</p>

        <h2>7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this website including the Mount Kush name, logo, mascot artwork, photography and copy is the intellectual property of Mount Kush and may not be reproduced without written consent.</p>

        <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush is not liable for any indirect, incidental or consequential damages arising from the use of our website or products. Our liability in any circumstance is limited to the value of the product purchased.</p>

        <h2>9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of South Africa. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of South Africa.</p>

        <h2>10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Continued use of this website after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

        <p style="margin-top:3rem; font-size:0.85rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">For any questions about these Terms, contact us on WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/27639260217" style="color:var(--gold-bright);">063 926 0217</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
